This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with video generation. It also involves the use of neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the evaluation of the proposed model using cross entropy, which is a common evaluation metric in multimedia (cs.MM) research. Finally, the use of neural flow models suggests that it could also belong to the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
